<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http - equiv = "Content-Type" content = "text/html">
    <title><TMPL_VAR REPORTNAME></title>
    <script src = "ChartNew.js"></script>
    <script src = "sorttable.js"></script>
    <link href = "master.css" rel = "stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class = "container">
<h3><TMPL_VAR REPORTNAME></h3>
<TMPL_VAR TODAY><hr>
<div class = "row">
This report displays the following transactions:
<ul>
<li> all the transfers into/out of the Rental account (excluding mortgage payments) </li>
<li>  all transactions that were made in other accounts to pay Rental expenses </li>
</ul> 
The total at the bottom should equal zero since all future paybacks are included. The total of all future paybacks<sup><a href="#fn1" id="ref1">1</a></sup> is $<TMPL_VAR "PAYBACKTOTAL">
<hr>
<table class = "table">
<thead>
    <tr>
        <th>ID</th>
        <th>Date</th>
        <th>Category</th>
        <th>Amount</th>
        <th>AccountName</th>
        <th>ToAccountName</th>
        <th>TransactionNumber</th>
        <th>Status</th>
        <th>Notes</th>

    </tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
    <TMPL_LOOP NAME=CONTENTS>
        <tr>
        <td class = "text-right"><TMPL_VAR "ID"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "Date"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "Category"></td>
        <td class = "money"><TMPL_VAR "Amount"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "AccountName"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "ToAccountName"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "TransactionNumber"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "Status"></td>
        <td><TMPL_VAR "Notes"></td>

        </tr>
    </TMPL_LOOP>
	<tr>
		<td> </td>
		<td> </td>
		<td class="text-right"><b>Total</b></td>
		<td class="money"><TMPL_VAR TOTAL></td>
	</tr>
</tbody>

</table>
</div>
<TMPL_LOOP ERRORS>
    <TMPL_VAR ERROR>
</TMPL_LOOP>
</div>
</div>
<sup id="fn1">1. Future paybacks are any future transaction marked void or followup<a href="#ref1" title="Jump back to footnote 1 in the text.">â†©</a></sup>
</body>
<script>
    <!-- Format double to base currency -->
    function currency(n) {
        n = parseFloat(n);
        n =  isNaN(n) ? 0 : n.toFixed(2);
        var out = n.toString().replace(".", "|");
        out = out.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, "<TMPL_VAR GROUP_SEPARATOR>");
        out = out.replace("|", "<TMPL_VAR DECIMAL_POINT>");
        return out;
    }
    var elements= document.getElementsByClassName("money");
    for (var i = 0; i < elements.length; i++) {
        var element = elements[i];
        element.style.textAlign='right';
        if (element.innerHTML.indexOf("-") > -1) {
            element.style.color="#ff0000";
        } 
        element.innerHTML = '<TMPL_VAR PFX_SYMBOL>' + currency(element.innerHTML) +'<TMPL_VAR SFX_SYMBOL>';
    }
</script>
</html>
